      • isKeywordSupported

        protected boolean isKeywordSupported()
        This method is used to check if the keyword can be handled in this special Processor.
        Returns:
        boolean, True, if the keyword can be handled here. False, if the keyword can not be handled here. But we will not set the status code to Failure, let other processors to handle.
